Product name: 6" Small BIRD SWING w/ EXTRA pieces
Description:
* Measures approximately 8" tall, including the quick links for hanging; the perch part measures approx. 6"
* Suitable for budgies, parakeets, parrotlets, lovebirds, cockatiels, and other small to medium parrots
* Contains a variety of shapes and materials on each "leg" of the swing, so it's like having toys on either side of the bird as he swings
* The two swings shown are representative of the item, but each swing may be unique in its parts.  Each "leg" will contain at least one apple branch piece and at least one pine block (dyed with food grade food coloring), along with other shapes such as round beads, oblong beads, spools, cubes, etc., along with bits of jute twine
* Quick Link is STAINLESS STEEL.   Beware of nickel plated hardware which often does contain small amounts of zinc and can be harmful to your bird!
* Wire is also stainless steel
* Each toy comes with several extra pieces so that you may refurbish the toy when your bird chews off a piece
These are the same toys I make for MY birds, using safe materials.  A variety of textures and shapes makes the toys more interesting to the birds, and having the soft pine which they can actually destroy over time makes for a very satisfied bird!
The extra pieces included enable you to refurbish the toy as needed and extend it's life.
Please remember that anything you give your bird may turn into a hazard!  Inspect all toys and other items frequently to be sure they are safe!
I can ship two of these (or a 6" swing and a small toy) for the same shipping cost, so it will pay to stock up!  Message me if you have special requests such as color and I'll be happy to see what I can do.  Excess shipping will be refunded - message me before you order if you would like a more accurate cost of shipping.
# SBS6S

Product name: Young Living Diffuser Repair Kit - Exact Match Replacement Part
Description:
Get your Young Living diffuser running again!! You can do it!! :)
4 SCREWS - 5 MINUTES - FIXED!
This is an exact factory matched ultrasonic element replacement kit for the Young Living rose inspired diffuser like the one pictured. 
(This repair kit does not include the diffuser)
If you are experiencing any of the following issues, this will likely solve the problem.
***Low water vapor output.
***Diffuser not working at all - light flashes once quickly, then shuts off.
The kit comes with everything required to make the repair.
***Detailed photo instructions
***A brand new ultrasonic element with plug and play connector (no cutting wires)
***A new silicone seal (prevent leaks)
***The proper screwdriver to do the repair
***Availability after the sale - feel free to contact me with any questions.
The repair method is simple...
 -(Detailed photo instructions are shipped along with the kit)
1. Remove the two screws on the bottom of the unit
2. Unplug the old transducer from the circuit board (the transducer sits at the bottom of the diffuser reservoir)
3. Remove the two screws from the underside of the black transducer cover at the bottom of the top half of the unit
4. Replace the transducer with the new element.
5. Replace the black cover and screws,
6. Re-assemble the unit and re-install the screws in the bottom of the unit.
7. Fill it up with water and your favorite Young Living oil
8. Enjoy
9. Relax
10. Unwind :)

Do you dream of cooking bacon that doesn’t shrink to half its size once its cooked? Does your bacon loving friend wish there was a better and cheaper way to make 1kg of bacon to eat all in one day?
